{"tid":769793,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】樂華邨爆水管 短褲港女後樓梯濕身玩水","createTime":"2018-08-06T13:00:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T03:33:37.000Z","uid":55851,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef50f4d0a9107abbfede9a9c2630313bbd35ad7","tid":769793,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"有圖：<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533215070_85cc.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180802%2Flarge%2F1533215070_85cc.jpg&d=LhGzDA2%2F6WhaJ9FLByg6IGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f69e3f6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180802/large/1533215070_85cc.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n有片：<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180802/58516887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58516887&d=LhGzDA2%2F6WhaJ9FLByg6IGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=59c37cad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F58516887&h=e6aa546a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180802/58516887</a><br />\n<br />\n 酷熱天氣警告發出好幾日，市民都有唔同消暑活動，不過牛頭角樂華邨有位女士就有特別方法消暑。話說星期二晚10點左右，樂華邨寧華樓11樓一條大廈淡水喉，懷疑用咗太多年終於抵受唔住壓力要爆，搞到大量淡水沿後樓梯湧落樓下。<br />\n<br />\n讀者陳先生表示，當日佢一上到樓就成地濕哂，於是沿着水流見到後樓梯「好似瀑布咁」，再望真啲發現有一個年約40歲嘅女士坐喺後樓梯地下。陳先生話當時以為位女士跣低，仲諗緊點幫手，但即刻就聽到幾下笑聲，原來佢喺度玩緊水。只見嗰位女士身穿黑色中袖衫同黑色短褲，紮起頭髮滿面笑容，手拍拍水又企起身，走上幾級再坐低擺post，之後仲用手機自拍，一副自得其樂模樣。<br />\n<br />\n不過，呢種方式似乎只有少數人識欣賞，陳先生話佢同其他街坊決定隔住防煙門睇呢位女士玩水，有人仲話唔明白點解咁開心。事關陳先生指因為爆水管關係，寧華樓2至11樓所有住戶都冇水用，佢自己到第二朝都要拎水桶落街攞水，雖然有啲唔方便，但佢讚房署處理爽手，唔到兩個鐘已經搵咗師傅維修，影響比想像中細。"},{"pid":"f176f3927fb45dcdecfd6ded186a46f3e1385d86","tid":769793,"uid":36253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"條腿好白滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb5eb1ae6ceef6309d84a2a4a2a91a93a0a1d90","tid":769793,"uid":18489,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:05:01.000Z","msg":"好樣哀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c9cb29d79a2ac69866b88877573416bdc53f08","tid":769793,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:08:54.000Z","msg":"我屌"},{"pid":"11d14f26e558bec8b2bfb9c83098ae435b594b7f","tid":769793,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"傻人出沒"},{"pid":"db2c2880f096f1f85e04a18482be6715214c6014","tid":769793,"uid":92690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d14f26e558bec8b2bfb9c83098ae435b594b7f","tid":769793,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"傻人出沒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T22:28:51.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2457bf6e934b7e75b5bb5473047fe69a8dab530","tid":769793,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T22:39:41.000Z","msg":"有望鏡頭喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a969b21b7ee1a612366eac2fa110400fc717755","tid":769793,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T22:41:47.000Z","msg":"去泳池咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"291c1e05c365dbfb902498bee273d9d54c506544","tid":769793,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f176f3927fb45dcdecfd6ded186a46f3e1385d86","tid":769793,"uid":36253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T13:01:26.000Z","msg":"條腿好白滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T23:00:51.000Z","msg":"係正喎個40歲師奶 真係想同佢一齊玩 扯扯地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：90後"},{"pid":"a4751bb824a20210de0f6e428bfa96b3ebca75f9","tid":